50|$|Mawlawi Mohammad Yunus Khalis (alternate spellings Yunis and Younas) (محمد يونس خالص; c. 1919 − July 19, 2006) was a mujahideen {{commander}} in Afghanistan during the Soviet invasion of Afghanistan. His party was called Hezb-i-Islami ("Party of Islam"), {{the same as}} Gulbuddin Hekmatyar's party. The two are commonly differentiated as Hezb-e Islami Khalis and <b>Hezb-e-Islami</b> Gulbuddin.|$|E
